            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"step-b-p3-with-thompson-sampling-on-the-simplex\">Step B \u2014 P3 with Thompson sampling on the simplex</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Same fit as the main <code>grp_pipeline_300m.py</code> notebook, replicated here so the comparison is self-contained: 3 nonlinear params (\u03b7, a, p) tuned via nested 5\u00d75 CV from <code>(\u03b7 \u2208 {0.5, 1, 2, 5, 10, 15, 20})</code>, <code>(a \u2208 linspace(0.5, 2.0, 8))</code>, <code>(p \u2208 {0.5, 1, 1.5, 2, 2.5, 3, 4})</code>; ridge \u03b1 from <code>(1, 3.16, 10, 31.6, ..., 10000)</code>; 39 signal coefs + 2 per-phase penalty coefs.</span></span>"
